        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2855877680" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10245749762737219642">I&apos;m not completely sure how I feel about this book. There were some parts that I really liked and some parts that made me laugh out loud, but then there were also some parts that annoyed me. Mostly Sara&apos;s way of thinking is what annoyed me. I&apos;m glad she came to her senses about what really mattered and what didn&apos;t. Maybe I just felt too old while reading this, maybe it was just a love/hate thing while reading.</span>
  <span id="freeText10245749762737219642" style="display:none">I'm not completely sure how I feel about this book. There were some parts that I really liked and some parts that made me laugh out loud, but then there were also some parts that annoyed me. Mostly Sara's way of thinking is what annoyed me. I'm glad she came to her senses about what really mattered and what didn't. Maybe I just felt too old while reading this, maybe it was just a love/hate thing while reading.</span>
