<li class='cover' id='bookCover_1672727'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1672727.Two_Way_Street"><img alt="Two-Way Street" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1381750633l/1672727._SX98_.jpg" />
